  <div class="c-entry-hero__content l-segment l-feature">
    
    
    <h1 class="c-page-title">I tried to write an essay about productivity in quarantine. It took me a month to do it.</h1>

    <p class="c-entry-summary p-dek">Americans feel pressured to work under the best of times. What happens during a pandemic?</p>

    <div class="c-byline">
  <span class="c-byline-wrapper">
    
      
        By
        <span class="c-byline__item">
          
            
            <a href="https://www.vox.com/authors/constance-grady" data-analytics-link="author-name"><span class="c-byline__author-name">Constance Grady</span></a><span class="c-byline__item"><a href="https://www.twitter.com/constancegrady" class="c-byline__twitter-handle">@constancegrady</a></span>
          
        </span>
      
      
      <span class="c-byline__item">
        
        <time class="c-byline__item" data-ui="timestamp" datetime="2020-04-17T14:00:00">
